Package org.blockchainnative.ethereum.metadata

Class EthereumMethodInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.blockchainnative.metadata.MethodInfo<EthereumParameterInfo>
      • org.blockchainnative.ethereum.metadata.EthereumMethodInfo
  • public class EthereumMethodInfo
extends MethodInfo<EthereumParameterInfo>
    Holds additional information about a smart contract method.

    It is recommended to use EthereumContractInfoBuilder to construct instances of this class.
    Since:
    1.0
    See Also:
    EthereumContractWrapperGenerator
